OL,3,CITV reporter reflects on
OL,4,Carchaeological find in Leicestershire
OL,6,FSometimes as a journalist, you report
OL,7,Fon a story and when you get there it
OL,8,Fturns into more of a story than you
OL,9,Fthought.
OL,11,FOn Sunday 21st July, myself and
OL,12,Fcameraman Jack Jones found ourselves
OL,13,Fat Willesley Scout campsite near Ashby-
OL,14,Fde-la-Zouch in Leicestershire.
