OL,3,CITV reporter reflects on
OL,4,Carchaeological find in Leicestershire
OL,6,FWe were filming a feature item about
OL,7,Fscouts from across the East Midlands
OL,8,Ftrying their hand at archaeology. The
OL,9,Fevent had been organised by Derbyshire
OL,10,FScout Archaeology Activity Team
OL,11,F(DSAT), a group founded by Morgause
OL,12,FLomas. Morgause was a scout herself
OL,13,Fand studied Archaeology at Cambridge
OL,14,FUniversity. She's now combined her
OL,15,Ftwin passions to inspire the next
OL,16,Fgeneration to go digging for history,
OL,17,Fand created a new Archaeology scout
OL,18,Fbadge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
