OL,3,CITV reporter reflects on
OL,4,Carchaeological find in Leicestershire
OL,6,FWillesley was an ideal location, as
OL,7,Fthe campsite sits on the remains of a
OL,8,FTudor manor-house which was knocked
OL,9,Fdown in 1953.
OL,11,FJack and I filmed the scouts
OL,12,Funcovering some of the foundations,
OL,13,Fand using their trowels and brushes to
OL,14,Fscour the brickwork for any items of
OL,15,Finterest.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
