OL,3,CITV reporter reflects on
OL,4,Carchaeological find in Leicestershire
OL,6,FFrom a news point of view, we were
OL,7,Fleft a bit in limbo. Normally, we
OL,8,Fwould have broadcast our report that
OL,9,Fsame day, but we were told the brooch
OL,10,Fwould have to go away to be examined
OL,11,Fand dated. We agreed to hold back from
OL,12,Fputting out a report and, like
OL,13,Feveryone else, spent the next few
OL,14,Fweeks on tenterhooks.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
