OL,3,CITV reporter reflects on
OL,4,Carchaeological find in Leicestershire
OL,6,FIn the end, it was the result
OL,7,Feverybody wanted. The Portable
OL,8,FAntiquities Scheme, based at the
OL,9,FBritish Museum, which keeps a record
OL,10,Fof public finds, confirmed the brooch
OL,11,Fwas genuine, Anglo-Saxon and around
OL,12,F1500 years old.
OL,14,FSometimes, it goes against your
OL,15,Finstinct as a journalist to sit on a
OL,16,Fstory - but sometimes it's well worth
OL,17,Fit!
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
